---
---

<section id="pourquoi" class="sec">
  <div class="sec-inner">
    <div class="why-grid">

      <div class="why-text fade-up">
        <span class="sec-label">Notre histoire</span>
        <h2 class="why-title">Marketing de qualité,<br>prix accessibles.</h2>
        <p class="why-p">Baptiste, Luca et Thybault ont fondé Com Roussillon en 2024 avec une conviction : <strong>les artisans et petites entreprises méritent une communication professionnelle</strong>, sans se ruiner ni s'y perdre.</p>
        <p class="why-p">Un seul interlocuteur, des devis clairs, des délais respectés. Pas de jargon, pas de surprise sur la facture.</p>
        <div class="why-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="btn-white">Parlons de votre projet</a>
          <a href="/notre-histoire" class="btn-text">Découvrir notre histoire →</a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="stats-wrap fade-up">
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-num">+30</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Clients accompagnés</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-num">2024</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Fondée à Perpignan</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-num">5★</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Note Google</span>
        </div>
        <div class="stat-item">
          <span class="stat-num">3</span>
          <span class="stat-label">Experts dédiés</span>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
#pourquoi { background: var(--dark) }

.why-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 6rem;
  align-items: center;
}

.why-title {
  font-size: clamp(2rem, 4vw, 3.2rem);
  font-weight: 600;
  line-height: 1.08;
  letter-spacing: -0.03em;
  color: #fff;
  margin-bottom: 1.4rem;
}

.why-p {
  font-size: 16px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #86868b;
  line-height: 1.75;
  margin-bottom: 1rem;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
}
.why-p strong { font-weight: 500; color: #e0e0e0 }

.why-ctas {
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  flex-wrap: wrap;
  gap: 1.2rem;
  margin-top: 2rem;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .why-ctas {
    flex-direction: column-reverse;
    align-items: flex-start;
  }
}

.btn-white {
  background: #fff;
  color: var(--dark);
  padding: .78rem 1.8rem;
  border-radius: 980px;
  font-size: 15px;
  font-weight: 500;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
  text-decoration: none;
  transition: background .2s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn-white:hover { background: #f0f0f0 }

.btn-text {
  color: #86868b;
  font-size: 14px;
  font-weight: 400;
  text-decoration: none;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
  transition: color .2s;
  white-space: nowrap;
}
.btn-text:hover { color: #fff }

/* Stats */
.stats-wrap {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
  gap: 0;
}

.stat-item {
  padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
  border: 0.5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  gap: .5rem;
}
.stat-item:nth-child(1) { border-top-left-radius: var(--radius) }
.stat-item:nth-child(2) { border-top-right-radius: var(--radius) }
.stat-item:nth-child(3) { border-bottom-left-radius: var(--radius) }
.stat-item:nth-child(4) { border-bottom-right-radius: var(--radius) }

.stat-num {
  font-size: 3.4rem;
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--gold);
  letter-spacing: -.04em;
  line-height: 1;
}

.stat-label {
  font-size: 13px;
  font-weight: 300;
  color: #86868b;
  letter-spacing: -.01em;
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .why-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 3rem }
  .stat-num { font-size: 2.8rem }
  .stat-item { padding: 1.8rem 1.4rem }
}
</style>
